                     <interp inst="t18090920-69-off393" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18090920-69-off393" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the 18th of September, a handkerchief, value 2 s. 6 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18090920-69-victim669" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Goodyear
                        <interp inst="t18090920-69-victim669" type="surname" value="Goodyear"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18090920-69-victim669" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18090920-69-victim669" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
